{"tid":1146034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"22歲女師課堂傳裸照！色誘男高中生「肉體交疊」…最高面臨20年徒刑","createTime":"2019-05-09T04:12:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T08:45:20.000Z","uid":72009,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"223b37c84df19e075a57c0d1f42682504e2abc32","tid":1146034,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T04:12:23.000Z","msg":"美國阿拉巴馬州一名在高中任教的22歲年輕女老師涉嫌多次分享自己的不雅照給2名男學生，還曾經和其中一名17歲的男同學發生性行為。她目前已經被學校解雇，檢警也正調查起訴，近日即將開庭審理；若有罪，她最高將面臨20年有期徒刑。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外電報導，22歲的高中女老師貝茨（Lyndsey Sherrod Bates）在特殊教育的高中任職，根據法庭曝光的內容指出，她在任教的過程中，曾多次和2名同校的男學生分享自己的裸照。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://pennswordtwo.com/custom/domain_1/image_files/sitemgr_photo_6650.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpennswordtwo.com%2Fcustom%2Fdomain_1%2Fimage_files%2Fsitemgr_photo_6650.jpg&h=2894d24a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46d166823143c27010fc1bcdb41154b9c4a38e56","tid":1146034,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T04:13:02.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"174c6063e0ccc238e0af80ff69fabbb877f576f2","tid":1146034,"uid":168730,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T04:13:07.000Z","msg":"快點色誘我"},{"pid":"55d0c5edc08b2847dd6b861f9ba34d9c7a186001","tid":1146034,"uid":94241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T04:13:12.000Z","msg":"特殊教育"},{"pid":"f657c03b30c8e4c536ad7d55e898a4ae07c89740","tid":1146034,"uid":32454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T04:14:02.000Z","msg":"快點"},{"pid":"34e4b36f2724e01617116555cd0ee528063b4241","tid":1146034,"uid":203543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T04:14:05.000Z","msg":"真。美女老師 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b307773c0452814e074c4f7723db93ebea6a546f","ti